      Calculator Web Application using Servlet and JSP

A basic web-based calculator developed using Java Servlets and JSP that performs arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. This project demonstrates form handling, request dispatching, and backend processing using the Servlet-JSP model.

ğŸ“Œ Overview
This project is a simple implementation of a calculator that:

Accepts two numeric inputs from the user html

Performs basic arithmetic operations

Displays the result on a dynamic JSP page

The goal is to demonstrate how Servlet and JSP can work together to build a dynamic web application using the Model-View-Controller (MVC) architecture.

